text:
During #forestfire hot ambers are carried by winds to homes located away from the fire front, catching those owners by surprise.

Protect your home: Use noncombustible mulch products, like rocks. Keep lawns irrigated. Keep gutters free of debris. Keep shrubs 5ft away.

#wildfire pic.twitter.com/Bgvlp7e7pj

text:
During #forestfire hot ambers are carried by winds to homes located away from the fire front, catching those owners by surprise.

Protect your home: Use noncombustible mulch products, like rocks. Keep lawns irrigated. Keep gutters free of debris. Keep shrubs 5ft away.

#wildfire pic.twitter.com/Bgvlp7e7pj

text:
#MountKenyaOnFire Update: 7.45PM:Fires in the south under control. Great work done by the men brought by @TropicAirKenya @kwskenya & @KeForestService.
